    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/ba166f3b4ec60496697cb85e22d5d68e.poster.avif?t=1763675801\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/ba166f3b4ec60496697cb85e22d5d68e.webm?t=1763675801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/ba166f3b4ec60496697cb85e22d5d68e.mp4?t=1763675801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>被战火吞噬的大陆！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战场女武神４》与系列首作《战场女武神》同属一个时代，但故事将聚焦在隶属于联邦军的E小队。小队队长库罗德‧沃雷斯与他的童年好友们将为了自由而投身于残酷的战场。但凛冽的暴风雪、如潮的帝国士兵与女武神那有如神明一般的力量，无一不是他们赢得胜利的巨大阻碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“BLiTZ”战斗系统与“CANVAS”图像引擎盛大回归！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※与其他机种版本的《战场女武神４》存在一定差异。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/ee798bb05a6e17c42fbd91f48b30b947.poster.avif?t=1763675801\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/ee798bb05a6e17c42fbd91f48b30b947.webm?t=1763675801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/ee798bb05a6e17c42fbd91f48b30b947.mp4?t=1763675801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/d19f890a18ad2df8bba24d4ab507019e.webp?t=1763675801\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <strong>战场上的青春故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过指挥热血的年轻指挥官“库罗德‧沃雷斯”、重型武器与工程学的天才“蕾莉‧米拉”、做事一根筋的达尔克斯人“拉兹”、冷若冰霜的王牌狙击手“凯伊‧舒伦”等众多个性丰富的角色展开故事。他们将亲眼目睹战争的残酷——冰冷战场之上E小队彼此之间的羁绊又将何去何从……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/69ceef3325130ab2909449a9e2efee17.webp?t=1763675801\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <strong>次世代的“BLiTZ”战斗系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合俯视角回合制策略、角色扮演和实时第三人称射击游戏要素的“BLiTZ”战斗系统重回战场。此外，更有全新兵种迫击炮兵、来自战舰的攻击・防御支援以及单位在濒死状态时可能触发的“英勇瞬间”等，种种全新功能同步搭载。不止如此，地图规模也将达到系列最大——面对帝国的威胁，指挥更加庞大的部队对抗他们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/680100a323590660e1a645830a8d570c.webp?t=1763675801\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <strong>搭载“CANVAS”图像引擎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系列标志性的手绘画风回归，并为次世代进行了全面革新。CANVAS图像引擎的创意来自水彩画作，将真实与幻想的视觉元素结合起来，呈现出风格明晰、色彩斑斓的世界。E小队的故事就将在这种可互动的绘画中进行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/6b038300f816d2e17791735623b93711.webp?t=1763675801\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <strong>传奇作曲家回归</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自初代起就曾担任《战场女武神》系列的作曲，其他更是着手了多款经典作品的作曲家——崎元仁先生，将回归《战场女武神》系列，为本作创作宏大的交响风格乐曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/2093ae270aaff40650907ae632428a4a.webp?t=1763675801\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <strong>PC版专享特别优化</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4K分辨率、取消帧率限制、可自定义的键盘与鼠标操作，甚至支持超宽屏显示。同时也将支持Steam成就与集换式卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790820/extras/0df0cc4c439b376cc53e2d201cbb96d3.webp?t=1763675801\" width=18 height=18 /></span> <strong>完全版</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战场女武神４ 最终版》中包含了游戏正篇以及所有可下载内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E小队，向大海前进！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >队长不在的E小队 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游击战斗　超级困难</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位女武神</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先行特别作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与第７小队的协同战线</p></li></ul>",
